'''Yavvitiri Spaceport''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on [[Yaga Minor/Legends|Yaga Minor]], several [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] from the [[Preparation Center]]. It had an isolated facility for diplomats and government officials.

